Andmete setup

netidf <- essee18 %>% 
  dplyr::select(netustm, agea, edulvlb, gndr, pspwght) 

netidf$Haridus <- car::recode(as.numeric((essee18$edulvlb)), "0:213='Kuni_phi'; 229='Kutse'; 313='Kesk'; 321:423='Kutse'; 520:800='Krg'; 5555=NA")
netidf$Haridus <- factor(netidf$Haridus, levels=c("Kuni_phi", "Kutse", "Kesk", "Krg", NA))

weightedMedian(essee18$netustm, w=netidf$pspwght, na.rm=TRUE)
## [1] 180
netidf$netbin [netidf$netustm <= 180] <- c("Alla_keskmise")
## Warning: Unknown or uninitialised column: `netbin`.
netidf$netbin [netidf$netustm > 180] <- c("le_keskmise")
netidf$netbin [is.na(netidf$netustm)] <- NA

netidf$netbin <- factor(netidf$netbin, levels = c("Alla_keskmise", "le_keskmise"))

wtd.quantile(essee18$netustm, q=c(0.25,0.5,0.75), na.rm = FALSE, weight=netidf$pspwght)
## 25% 50% 75% 
## 120 180 360
netidf$netmult [essee18$netustm <= 120] <- c("Madal")
## Warning: Unknown or uninitialised column: `netmult`.
netidf$netmult [essee18$netustm <= 180 & essee18$netustm > 120] <- c("Madal-keskmine")
netidf$netmult [essee18$netustm <= 360 & essee18$netustm > 180] <- c("Krge-keskmine")
netidf$netmult [essee18$netustm > 360] <- c("Krge")
netidf$netmult [is.na(netidf$netustm)] <- NA
netidf$netmult <- factor(netidf$netmult, levels = c("Madal", "Madal-keskmine", "Krge-keskmine", "Krge"))

netidf$gndr <- car::recode(as.numeric(netidf$gndr), "1='Mees'; 2='Naine'")

#remove NA-s and 1s 
netidf <- netidf %>% 
  filter(netustm != 1)
